    {
      "id": "E:note:row437958:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "TITLE:    ISSUES:    - Left distal femur fracture    - Right tib-fib fracture   ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row437958#s1",
      "text": "TITLE:    ISSUES:    - Left distal femur fracture    - Right tib-fib fracture    - Mesenteric hematoma    - Multiple rib fractures    - Sternal fracture    - T8 vertebral body fracture    .    24 HOUR EVENTS:    [**12-15**]: foley replaced; vanco to continue for the next 2 days -> then    switch to nafcillin for MSSA pna; TF held in anticipation of OR --> to    go [**12-16**] with trauma for trach/PED/IVC; IVF changed to D51/2NS w/K as Na    rising    Trauma, s/p (see above)    Assessment:    Hct down to 22.7 (24), pedal pulses dopplerable/good cap refill in both    [**Name (NI) **], pt still able to move all extremitites purposefully."
    },
